{"tid":1869153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日3點火炭啊","createTime":"2020-02-08T04:23:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T04:50:54.000Z","uid":105103,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ab2652d2c42dcb00469bc2ebcb4893a38c69c83b","tid":1869153,"uid":105103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:23:25.000Z","msg":"1117 手足：火炭駿洋一手<br />\n平時地盤只有幾隻膠馬阻住，現在沿住山尾街一路上黃竹洋街全部防暴水馬、衝鋒車加便衣不停巡邏，黃竹洋街迴旋處更加設立警崗，截查所有上黃竹洋村嘅車輛。<br />\n<br />\n由於聽日已經係星期日，火炭一般會比較靜，以火炭嘅地理位置，差佬只需要封咗火炭路， 基本上成個火炭區，佢要坑殺任何人都冇人知。<br />\n<br />\n我好有理由懷疑差佬會趁聽日，人流少嘅時間，不停將需要隔離嘅人車入火炭。<br />\n<br />\n網上完全冇任何聲音講火炭嘅環境， 大家真係信需要隔離嘅人唔會走到出嚟，好撚乖喺個空盪盪嘅清水樓入面過兩個禮拜？<br />\n<br />\n1030 黃竹洋街軍裝開始清車， 估計需要運送物資入去嚟已經<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家諗住點做呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eab7c8bd31a3d0a6da73932d6bdd16d9182b995f","tid":1869153,"uid":105103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:25:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"336bf2d57278e9248914323e55d0938b5b79c0a6","tid":1869153,"uid":44358,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:26:58.000Z","msg":"如果你唔係咳嗽師，又或者武漢返嚟，又或者係潛在帶病者。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔建議你去火炭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黑警係需要冠狀病毒，而唔係手足送頭。"},{"pid":"95f82e6d25c9e8632c0970c6ab1bd0c4e657a0a3","tid":1869153,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:27:30.000Z","msg":"仲以為你話排口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f82c6776be8a2d41ea266cc83d0e204b18ece221","tid":1869153,"uid":51790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:30:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">又呃人送頭<br />\n係做嘢嘅出街狩獵支那人好過啦</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"fda19f8450896eba1897eee0f66f753220286879","tid":1869153,"uid":42650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:31:10.000Z","msg":"今朝10:30經過實況<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W4Gicc4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW4Gicc4.png&h=9cfef375&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49c7fa461595ce664e17ea29a8b51a9a26c778fd","tid":1869153,"uid":109629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:50:54.000Z","msg":"星期六火炭已經靜好多架喇 有咩動作都會好顯眼<br />\n<br />\n利申火炭返工 (而家返緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"}]}